    <item>
      <title>辨太阳病脉证并治法下：一五五</title>
      <link>https://acuherb.xyz/posts/shanghanlun-155/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Jun 2025 19:43:22 +0800</pubDate><author>124768092@qq.com (AcuHerb)</author>
      <guid>https://acuherb.xyz/posts/shanghanlun-155/</guid>
      <category domain="https://acuherb.xyz/categories/%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E7%97%85%E4%B8%8B/">太阳病下</category>
      <description>&lt;h2 class=&#34;heading-element&#34; id=&#34;一五五病在阳应以汗解之反以冷水潠之若灌之其热被劫不得去弥更益烦肉上粟起意欲饮水反不渴者服文蛤散-若不差者与五苓散&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;一五五：病在阳，应以汗解之，反以冷水潠之，若灌之，其热被劫不得去，弥更益烦，肉上粟起，意欲饮水，反不渴者，服「文蛤散 」：若不差者，与「五苓散」。&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;#%e4%b8%80%e4%ba%94%e4%ba%94%e7%97%85%e5%9c%a8%e9%98%b3%e5%ba%94%e4%bb%a5%e6%b1%97%e8%a7%a3%e4%b9%8b%e5%8f%8d%e4%bb%a5%e5%86%b7%e6%b0%b4%e6%bd%a0%e4%b9%8b%e8%8b%a5%e7%81%8c%e4%b9%8b%e5%85%b6%e7%83%ad%e8%a2%ab%e5%8a%ab%e4%b8%8d%e5%be%97%e5%8e%bb%e5%bc%a5%e6%9b%b4%e7%9b%8a%e7%83%a6%e8%82%89%e4%b8%8a%e7%b2%9f%e8%b5%b7%e6%84%8f%e6%ac%b2%e9%a5%ae%e6%b0%b4%e5%8f%8d%e4%b8%8d%e6%b8%b4%e8%80%85%e6%9c%8d%e6%96%87%e8%9b%a4%e6%95%a3-%e8%8b%a5%e4%b8%8d%e5%b7%ae%e8%80%85%e4%b8%8e%e4%ba%94%e8%8b%93%e6%95%a3&#34; class=&#34;heading-mark&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;svg class=&#34;octicon octicon-link&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 16 16&#34; version=&#34;1.1&#34; width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;</description>
