    <item>
      <title>辨太阳病脉证并治法下：一五四</title>
      <link>https://acuherb.xyz/posts/shanghanlun-154/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Jun 2025 18:59:22 +0800</pubDate><author>124768092@qq.com (AcuHerb)</author>
      <guid>https://acuherb.xyz/posts/shanghanlun-154/</guid>
      <category domain="https://acuherb.xyz/categories/%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E7%97%85%E4%B8%8B/">太阳病下</category>
      <description>&lt;h2 class=&#34;heading-element&#34; id=&#34;一五四太阳病下之其脉浮不结胸者此为欲解也脉促者必结胸也脉细数者必咽痛脉弦者必两胁拘急脉紧者头痛未止脉沉紧者必心下痛脉沉滑者协热利-脉数滑者必下血&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;一五四：太阳病，下之，其脉浮，不结胸者，此为欲解也；脉促者，必结胸也；脉细数者，必咽痛：脉弦者，必两胁拘急；脉紧者，头痛未止脉沉紧者，必心下痛；脉沉滑者，「协热利」； 脉数滑者，必下血。&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;#%e4%b8%80%e4%ba%94%e5%9b%9b%e5%a4%aa%e9%98%b3%e7%97%85%e4%b8%8b%e4%b9%8b%e5%85%b6%e8%84%89%e6%b5%ae%e4%b8%8d%e7%bb%93%e8%83%b8%e8%80%85%e6%ad%a4%e4%b8%ba%e6%ac%b2%e8%a7%a3%e4%b9%9f%e8%84%89%e4%bf%83%e8%80%85%e5%bf%85%e7%bb%93%e8%83%b8%e4%b9%9f%e8%84%89%e7%bb%86%e6%95%b0%e8%80%85%e5%bf%85%e5%92%bd%e7%97%9b%e8%84%89%e5%bc%a6%e8%80%85%e5%bf%85%e4%b8%a4%e8%83%81%e6%8b%98%e6%80%a5%e8%84%89%e7%b4%a7%e8%80%85%e5%a4%b4%e7%97%9b%e6%9c%aa%e6%ad%a2%e8%84%89%e6%b2%89%e7%b4%a7%e8%80%85%e5%bf%85%e5%bf%83%e4%b8%8b%e7%97%9b%e8%84%89%e6%b2%89%e6%bb%91%e8%80%85%e5%8d%8f%e7%83%ad%e5%88%a9-%e8%84%89%e6%95%b0%e6%bb%91%e8%80%85%e5%bf%85%e4%b8%8b%e8%a1%80&#34; class=&#34;heading-mark&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;svg class=&#34;octicon octicon-link&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 16 16&#34; version=&#34;1.1&#34; width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;</description>
