    <item>
      <title>辨太阳病脉证并治法下：一五三</title>
      <link>https://acuherb.xyz/posts/shanghanlun-153/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Jun 2025 18:21:22 +0800</pubDate><author>124768092@qq.com (AcuHerb)</author>
      <guid>https://acuherb.xyz/posts/shanghanlun-153/</guid>
      <category domain="https://acuherb.xyz/categories/%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E7%97%85%E4%B8%8B/">太阳病下</category>
      <description>&lt;h2 class=&#34;heading-element&#34; id=&#34;一五三太阳病二三曰不能卧但欲起心下必结脉微弱者本有久寒也反下之若利之必作结胸未止者四日复下之此作协热利也&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;一五三：「太阳病」，二三曰，不能卧，但欲起，心下必结，脉微弱者，本有久寒也，反下之，若利之，必作「结胸」；未止者，四日复下之，此作「协热利」也。&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;#%e4%b8%80%e4%ba%94%e4%b8%89%e5%a4%aa%e9%98%b3%e7%97%85%e4%ba%8c%e4%b8%89%e6%9b%b0%e4%b8%8d%e8%83%bd%e5%8d%a7%e4%bd%86%e6%ac%b2%e8%b5%b7%e5%bf%83%e4%b8%8b%e5%bf%85%e7%bb%93%e8%84%89%e5%be%ae%e5%bc%b1%e8%80%85%e6%9c%ac%e6%9c%89%e4%b9%85%e5%af%92%e4%b9%9f%e5%8f%8d%e4%b8%8b%e4%b9%8b%e8%8b%a5%e5%88%a9%e4%b9%8b%e5%bf%85%e4%bd%9c%e7%bb%93%e8%83%b8%e6%9c%aa%e6%ad%a2%e8%80%85%e5%9b%9b%e6%97%a5%e5%a4%8d%e4%b8%8b%e4%b9%8b%e6%ad%a4%e4%bd%9c%e5%8d%8f%e7%83%ad%e5%88%a9%e4%b9%9f&#34; class=&#34;heading-mark&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;svg class=&#34;octicon octicon-link&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 16 16&#34; version=&#34;1.1&#34; width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;</description>
