      <description>&lt;h2 class=&#34;heading-element&#34; id=&#34;一五一太阳病重发汗而复下之不大便五六日舌上燥而渴日哺所小有潮热从心下至少腹鞭满而痛不可近者大陷胸汤主之&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;一五一：「太阳病」，重发汗，而复下之，不大便五六日，舌上燥而渴，日哺所小有潮热，从心下至少腹鞭满而痛不可近者，「大陷胸汤」主之。&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;#%e4%b8%80%e4%ba%94%e4%b8%80%e5%a4%aa%e9%98%b3%e7%97%85%e9%87%8d%e5%8f%91%e6%b1%97%e8%80%8c%e5%a4%8d%e4%b8%8b%e4%b9%8b%e4%b8%8d%e5%a4%a7%e4%be%bf%e4%ba%94%e5%85%ad%e6%97%a5%e8%88%8c%e4%b8%8a%e7%87%a5%e8%80%8c%e6%b8%b4%e6%97%a5%e5%93%ba%e6%89%80%e5%b0%8f%e6%9c%89%e6%bd%ae%e7%83%ad%e4%bb%8e%e5%bf%83%e4%b8%8b%e8%87%b3%e5%b0%91%e8%85%b9%e9%9e%ad%e6%bb%a1%e8%80%8c%e7%97%9b%e4%b8%8d%e5%8f%af%e8%bf%91%e8%80%85%e5%a4%a7%e9%99%b7%e8%83%b8%e6%b1%a4%e4%b8%bb%e4%b9%8b&#34; class=&#34;heading-mark&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;svg class=&#34;octicon octicon-link&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 16 16&#34; version=&#34;1.1&#34; width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;</description>
