    <item>
      <title>辨太阳病脉证并治法下：一五〇</title>
      <link>https://acuherb.xyz/posts/shanghanlun-150/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Jun 2025 16:51:22 +0800</pubDate><author>124768092@qq.com (AcuHerb)</author>
      <guid>https://acuherb.xyz/posts/shanghanlun-150/</guid>
      <category domain="https://acuherb.xyz/categories/%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E7%97%85%E4%B8%8B/">太阳病下</category>
      <description>&lt;h2 class=&#34;heading-element&#34; id=&#34;一五伤寒十余日热结在里复往来寒热者与大柴胡汤但结胸无太热者此与水结在胸胁也但头微汗出者大陷胸汤主之&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;一五〇：「伤寒」十余日，热结在里，复往来寒热者，与「大柴胡汤」。但「结胸」无太热者，此与水结在胸胁也，但头微汗出者，「大陷胸汤」主之。&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;#%e4%b8%80%e4%ba%94%e4%bc%a4%e5%af%92%e5%8d%81%e4%bd%99%e6%97%a5%e7%83%ad%e7%bb%93%e5%9c%a8%e9%87%8c%e5%a4%8d%e5%be%80%e6%9d%a5%e5%af%92%e7%83%ad%e8%80%85%e4%b8%8e%e5%a4%a7%e6%9f%b4%e8%83%a1%e6%b1%a4%e4%bd%86%e7%bb%93%e8%83%b8%e6%97%a0%e5%a4%aa%e7%83%ad%e8%80%85%e6%ad%a4%e4%b8%8e%e6%b0%b4%e7%bb%93%e5%9c%a8%e8%83%b8%e8%83%81%e4%b9%9f%e4%bd%86%e5%a4%b4%e5%be%ae%e6%b1%97%e5%87%ba%e8%80%85%e5%a4%a7%e9%99%b7%e8%83%b8%e6%b1%a4%e4%b8%bb%e4%b9%8b&#34; class=&#34;heading-mark&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;svg class=&#34;octicon octicon-link&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 16 16&#34; version=&#34;1.1&#34; width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;</description>
