      <description>&lt;h2 class=&#34;heading-element&#34; id=&#34;一四二问曰病有结胸有藏结其状何如答曰按之痛寸脉浮关脉沉名曰结胸也何谓藏结答曰如结胸状饮食如故时时下利寸脉浮关脉小细沉紧名曰藏结舌上自苔滑者难治&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;一四二：问曰：病有「结胸」，有「藏结」，其状何如？答曰：按之痛，寸脉浮，关脉沉，名曰「结胸」也。何谓「藏结」？答曰：如「结胸」状，饮食如故，时时下利，寸脉浮，关脉小细沉紧，名曰「藏结」；舌上自苔滑者，难治。&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;#%e4%b8%80%e5%9b%9b%e4%ba%8c%e9%97%ae%e6%9b%b0%e7%97%85%e6%9c%89%e7%bb%93%e8%83%b8%e6%9c%89%e8%97%8f%e7%bb%93%e5%85%b6%e7%8a%b6%e4%bd%95%e5%a6%82%e7%ad%94%e6%9b%b0%e6%8c%89%e4%b9%8b%e7%97%9b%e5%af%b8%e8%84%89%e6%b5%ae%e5%85%b3%e8%84%89%e6%b2%89%e5%90%8d%e6%9b%b0%e7%bb%93%e8%83%b8%e4%b9%9f%e4%bd%95%e8%b0%93%e8%97%8f%e7%bb%93%e7%ad%94%e6%9b%b0%e5%a6%82%e7%bb%93%e8%83%b8%e7%8a%b6%e9%a5%ae%e9%a3%9f%e5%a6%82%e6%95%85%e6%97%b6%e6%97%b6%e4%b8%8b%e5%88%a9%e5%af%b8%e8%84%89%e6%b5%ae%e5%85%b3%e8%84%89%e5%b0%8f%e7%bb%86%e6%b2%89%e7%b4%a7%e5%90%8d%e6%9b%b0%e8%97%8f%e7%bb%93%e8%88%8c%e4%b8%8a%e8%87%aa%e8%8b%94%e6%bb%91%e8%80%85%e9%9a%be%e6%b2%bb&#34; class=&#34;heading-mark&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;svg class=&#34;octicon octicon-link&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 16 16&#34; version=&#34;1.1&#34; width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;</description>
