      <description>&lt;h2 class=&#34;heading-element&#34; id=&#34;一三八太阳病六七日表证乃在下之脉微而沉反不结胸其人发狂者以热在下焦少腹当鞭满小便自利者下血乃愈所以然者以太阳随经瘀热在裹故也抵当汤主之&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;一三八：「太阳病」，六七日表证乃在，下之，脉微而沉，反不结胸其人发狂者，以热在下焦，少腹当鞭满，小便自利者，下血乃愈。所以然者，以「太阳」随经，瘀热在裹故也。「抵当汤」主之。&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;#%e4%b8%80%e4%b8%89%e5%85%ab%e5%a4%aa%e9%98%b3%e7%97%85%e5%85%ad%e4%b8%83%e6%97%a5%e8%a1%a8%e8%af%81%e4%b9%83%e5%9c%a8%e4%b8%8b%e4%b9%8b%e8%84%89%e5%be%ae%e8%80%8c%e6%b2%89%e5%8f%8d%e4%b8%8d%e7%bb%93%e8%83%b8%e5%85%b6%e4%ba%ba%e5%8f%91%e7%8b%82%e8%80%85%e4%bb%a5%e7%83%ad%e5%9c%a8%e4%b8%8b%e7%84%a6%e5%b0%91%e8%85%b9%e5%bd%93%e9%9e%ad%e6%bb%a1%e5%b0%8f%e4%be%bf%e8%87%aa%e5%88%a9%e8%80%85%e4%b8%8b%e8%a1%80%e4%b9%83%e6%84%88%e6%89%80%e4%bb%a5%e7%84%b6%e8%80%85%e4%bb%a5%e5%a4%aa%e9%98%b3%e9%9a%8f%e7%bb%8f%e7%98%80%e7%83%ad%e5%9c%a8%e8%a3%b9%e6%95%85%e4%b9%9f%e6%8a%b5%e5%bd%93%e6%b1%a4%e4%b8%bb%e4%b9%8b&#34; class=&#34;heading-mark&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;svg class=&#34;octicon octicon-link&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 16 16&#34; version=&#34;1.1&#34; width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;</description>
