    <item>
      <title>辨太阳病脉证并治法下：一三七</title>
      <link>https://acuherb.xyz/posts/shanghanlun-137/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Jun 2025 10:27:22 +0800</pubDate><author>124768092@qq.com (AcuHerb)</author>
